### Aurelia API — SPR

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@parameterId = REPLACE_WITH_PARAMETER_ID
@recordId = REPLACE_WITH_RECORD_ID

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Catalogs
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### List SPR measure groups
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/groups

### List SPR units
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/units

### List SPR parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/parameters

### List SPR assignments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/assignments

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Monthly records
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create monthly record
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/monthly-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parameterId": "{{parameterId}}",
  "periodYear": 2026,
  "periodMonth": 6,
  "numericValue": 123.45,
  "notes": "Registro mensual SPR de prueba"
}

### List monthly records
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/monthly-records

### List monthly records by period
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/monthly-records?periodYear=2026&periodMonth=6

### Get monthly record by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/monthly-records/{{recordId}}

### Update monthly record value
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/monthly-records/{{recordId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "numericValue": 150.75,
  "notes": "Valor actualizado"
}

### Submit monthly record
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/monthly-records/{{recordId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "submitted",
  "notes": "Enviado para revisión"
}

### Approve monthly record
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/spr/monthly-records/{{recordId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "approved",
  "notes": "Aprobado"
}
